code: import{Axios}from'./Axios';function getExams(){return Axios.get('/api/category');}function getExamById(id){return Axios.get("/api/category/".concat(id));}function getQuestions(id){return Axios.get("/api/question/getQuestionByExamId/".concat(id));}function addQuestions(payload){return Axios.post("/api/calculator/",payload);}function getResult(idUser,idExam){return Axios.get("/api/result/getResultByExamAndUser/".concat(idUser,"/").concat(idExam));}function getAllResult(idUser){return Axios.get("/api/result/getAllResultByUser/".concat(idUser));}function getRanking(){return Axios.get("/api/result/ranking");}export var examsServices={getExams:getExams,getExamById:getExamById,getQuestions:getQuestions,addQuestions:addQuestions,getResult:getResult,getAllResult:getAllResult,getRanking:getRanking};
